Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: On the 40th anniversary of the United Nations
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydpcc
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 20 Sep 1985
The 40th anniversary of the United Nations, the history of the organisation, and the security arrangements for the 1985 meeting of the Security Council in New York.